Titolo: Arsenal of Democracy (video game)

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Arsenal of Democracy is a grand strategy wargame that is based on Hearts of Iron II - Armageddon and its Europa Engine. It is developed by BL-Logic, a development studio made up by fans of the Hearts of Iron series and active members of the modding community. Arsenal of Democracy was announced on September 8, 2009 and released on February 23, 2010.As in other games in the grand strategy Hearts of Iron series, Arsenal of Democracy allows for the player take control of and manage nearly any World War II and early Cold War era nation-state including its political, diplomatic, espionage, economic, military, and technological aspects.